Table Name: trx_sales_order

Description: Represents a sales order transaction created by a customer. 

Table Type: Transaction (trx_) 

Domain: sales

primary key - id - sales

FK - id_sales_status - ref_sales_status

main coluns:
order_date
total_amount
created_at
updated_at

used by:
backend api
frontend
reports

notes: ordes are immutable after status = completed
